{"tid":724040,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]點解淨係得中東三寶先玩得起A380","createTime":"2018-06-30T17:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T09:08:13.000Z","uid":98467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0838259057d4156916d0398963023854dcbe09dc","tid":724040,"uid":98467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"點解Emirates一買就可以買50架380,好似完全唔需要考慮<br />\n但其他公司都開始逐步淘汰A380,好似新航都唔再續租,搞到兩架380要拆件賣<br />\n但中東三寶好似完全唔驚重繼續買380,到底邊度嚟咁多客源去養咁多架A380<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cd01468896d1a7f191002b8c6799742ce1509f","tid":724040,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"屋企人去泰國，坐呢間野嘅A380，幾正，仲便過國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbbe49a562c487750dfdbb75c2b77602956204f","tid":724040,"uid":61257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"人地大把錢<br />\n<br />\n摩天大廈又係佢最高<br />\n<br />\n油唔洗錢既<br />\n<br />\n皇馬阿記天價心口冠名贊助<br />\n<br />\n當宣傳自己國家"},{"pid":"66b167818c6c7549a3ea12c4543c2869ca87913e","tid":724040,"uid":61782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"先唔講客量夠唔夠坐<br />\n機場已經係一個好大嘅制肘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港機場有橋而又泊得A380好似唔夠10個<br />\n而且得一個閘口有三條橋<br />\n<br />\n新航唔係開始退或者減少啲A380<br />\n只係嫌佢舊要換新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢半年有四部新A380<br />\n同時間退租左四部飛左十年嘅A380"},{"pid":"b9f0a24e4e43f20dc28b12adaa9e6b65c091882a","tid":724040,"uid":4596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T23:45:40.000Z","msg":"因為油唔使錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358140b558ac07c444daf4a1b6ad293d39a90206","tid":724040,"uid":9732,"like":0,"d